{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839971083,"sessionID":"ses_287b0bd74ffex025KouS6wmw08","part":{"id":"prt_d784f849f0012Ks4nW8uyA2I40","messageID":"msg_d784f70c0001iWR7jslU55122p","sessionID":"ses_287b0bd74ffex025KouS6wmw08","type":"tool","tool":"glob","callID":"toolu_tool-bd97d131e0674a85bdc740ae822920dd","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"pattern":"**/pkg/apis/**/*.go"},"output":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types.go\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/deepcopy.go\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/doc.go\n/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go","metadata":{"count":5,"truncated":false},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z","time":{"start":1775839971067,"end":1775839971081}}}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839971090,"sessionID":"ses_287b0bd74ffex025KouS6wmw08","part":{"id":"prt_d784f86dc0012Qtufz1XW5rvaq","messageID":"msg_d784f70c0001iWR7jslU55122p","sessionID":"ses_287b0bd74ffex025KouS6wmw08","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-35e06b59401643d4abc58863471bd9b6","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AgentCube Runtime API\n2: \n3: This package contains the Kubernetes API definitions for the AgentCube runtime resources.\n4: \n5: ## API Group\n6: \n7: - **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n8: - **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n9: - **Kind**: `AgentRuntime`\n10: \n11: ## Types\n12: \n13: ### AgentRuntime\n14: \n15: `AgentRuntime` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a sandbox orchestration runtime for managing the lifecycle of agent pods.\n16: \n17: #### Spec\n18: \n19: The `AgentRuntimeSpec` defines the desired state of an AgentRuntime:\n20: \n21: - **PodTemplate** (*SandboxTemplate, required): Template for creating sandbox pods\n22: - **SessionTimeout** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Timeout for idle sessions before cleanup (default: 15m)\n23: - **MaxSessionDuration** (*metav1.Duration, optional): Maximum allowed duration for a session (default: 8h)\n24: \n25: #### Status\n26: \n27: The `AgentRuntimeStatus` defines the observed state of an AgentRuntime:\n28: \n29: - **Conditions** ([]metav1.Condition, optional): List of conditions representing the runtime state\n30: - **ObservedGeneration** (int64, optional): Most recent generation observed by the controller\n31: \n32: ### SandboxTemplate\n33: \n34: Defines the template for creating sandbox pods:\n35: \n36: - **Metadata** (*SandboxMetadata, optional): Labels and annotations for the pod\n37: - **Spec** (SandboxPodSpec, required): Pod specification\n38: \n39: ### SandboxPodSpec\n40: \n41: Defines the pod specification for sandbox pods:\n42: \n43: - **Containers** ([]SandboxContainer, required): List of containers in the pod\n44: - **NodeSelector** (map[string]string, optional): Node selection constraints\n45: - **Affinity** (*SandboxAffinity, optional): Pod scheduling constraints\n46: - **Tolerations** ([]SandboxToleration, optional): Pod tolerations\n47: - **ResourceRequirements** (*SandboxResources, optional): Resource requirements for the pod\n48: - **Volumes** ([]SandboxVolume, optional): Pod volumes\n49: \n50: ## Usage\n51: \n52: ### Creating an AgentRuntime\n53: \n54: ```yaml\n55: apiVersion: runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1\n56: kind: AgentRuntime\n57: metadata:\n58:   name: example-runtime\n59:   namespace: default\n60: spec:\n61:   podTemplate:\n62:     spec:\n63:       containers:\n64:       - name: agent\n65:         image: agent:latest\n66:         ports:\n67:         - containerPort: 8080\n68: ```\n69: \n70: ### Using with client-go\n71: \n72: ```go\n73: import (\n74:     \"context\"\n75:     \n76:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1\"\n77:     \"github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go/clientset/versioned\"\n78:     metav1 \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1\"\n79: )\n80: \n81: func createAgentRuntime(clientset *versioned.Clientset) error {\n82:     runtime := &v1alpha1.AgentRuntime{\n83:         ObjectMeta: metav1.ObjectMeta{\n84:             Name:      \"example-runtime\",\n85:             Namespace: \"default\",\n86:         },\n87:         Spec: v1alpha1.AgentRuntimeSpec{\n88:             PodTemplate: &v1alpha1.SandboxTemplate{\n89:                 Spec: v1alpha1.SandboxPodSpec{\n90:                     Containers: []v1alpha1.SandboxContainer{\n91:                         {\n92:                             Name:  \"agent\",\n93:                             Image: \"agent:latest\",\n94:                         },\n95:                     },\n96:                 },\n97:             },\n98:         },\n99:     }\n100:     \n101:     _, err := clientset.RuntimeV1alpha1().AgentRuntimes(\"default\").Create(\n102:         context.TODO(),\n103:         runtime,\n104:         metav1.CreateOptions{},\n105:     )\n106:     return err\n107: }\n108: ```\n109: \n110: ## Testing\n111: \n112: Run the unit tests:\n113: \n114: ```bash\n115: go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...\n116: ```\n117: \n118: ## CRD Installation\n119: \n120: The CRD YAML file is located at `config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml`.\n121: \n122: Install the CRD:\n123: \n124: ```bash\n125: kubectl apply -f config/crd/bases/runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh_agentruntimes.yaml\n126: ```\n127: \n128: Verify installation:\n129: \n130: ```bash\n131: kubectl get crd agentruntimes.runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n132: ```\n133: \n134: ## Features\n135: \n136: - **Kubernetes-native**: Leverages Kubernetes CRD and controller patterns\n137: - **Type-safe**: Generated Go types for compile-time safety\n138: - **Extensible**: Supports custom pod templates, volumes, and configurations\n139: - **Status tracking**: Built-in conditions for runtime state management\n140: - **Resource management**: Support for resource limits, requests, and scheduling constraints\n141: - **Security**: Full support for security contexts, capabilities, and seccomp profiles\n142: \n143: ## License\n144: \n145: Copyright 2024 Volcano Authors.\n\n(End of file - total 145 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AgentCube Runtime API\n\nThis package contains the Kubernetes API definitions for the AgentCube runtime resources.\n\n## API Group\n\n- **Group**: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh`\n- **Version**: `v1alpha1`\n- **Kind**: `AgentRuntime`\n\n## Types\n\n### AgentRuntime\n\n`AgentRuntime` is a Kubernetes custom resource that defines a sandbox orchestration runtime for managing the lifecycle of agent pods.\n\n#### Spec\n\nThe `AgentRuntimeSpec` defines the desired state of an AgentRuntime:\n","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-4.7_20260410T163120Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/README.md","time":{"start":1775839971071,"end":1775839971088}}}}
